title: Crew Show!
description:
Matt has been driving several fast Porsche products. He spent a week with the new Cayman GT4 and lets us know if they've fixed the gearing. Then he spent a day with the Cayenne GTS, Porsche's new truck coupe. Zack went for a drive in a supercharged F-150 that was full of power and odd shwag. He's not sure about the price. Plus, more Supra talk. 

Watch the show at: https://youtu.be/fIqJ_BUaksY
